      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
